This song and whole album is a masterpiece!! Nicki's bars were genius and all the word play was brilliant!! You can definitely tell she is incredibly intelligent and has a lot of wisdom!! Her flow and technique is flawless!! She spit so effortlessly and fluently!! Her breathe control is perfect and she articulates her lyrics very clearly!! Nicki is so versatile the way she constantly and smoothly switches up her flow is impeccable!! Nicki gave us rap, pop, dance music, afrobeat and R&B all in one album!! love it!! Pink Friday 2 is fire 🔥 and I'm definitely here for it!! I think she did an amazing job!! Nicki righteously deserves the title of "Queen" and this album absolutely proves that!!

I absolutely love this song!! I keep listening to it over and over!! I don't like some of the newer hip-hop that is out nowadays!! To me it's lost a lot of resemblance of what it use to be but this song was great and makes me feel good!! That's also why I love Nicki so much because she has always stayed true to the art!! True hip-hop is about meaningful and intelligent bars!! The ability to tell a story in their music that people can relate too! Nicki brings all the good qualities and traits of old school plus the ability to incorporate new school hip-hop by keeping her beats and lyrics fresh!! Nicki did an amazing job!! This song is definitely a hit!!
